  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a cataplana vessel over medium-high heat",
    "Add the chicken to the vessel and cook until browned, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger to the vessel and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the yuzu juice, soy sauce, and gochujang to the vessel and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes",
    "Stir in the chopped scallions and sesame seeds",
    "Season the mixture with salt and black pepper to taste",
    "Serve the stir-fry hot, garnished with additional scallions and sesame seeds if desired"
  ],
